thread.title: The 10-Point.

author: Gerard Baker
title: The 10-Point.
text:
Good morning,
March Madness
Washington is set for another busy week with members of President Trump’s own party contemplating legislation to thwart his “America First” tariffs, a proposal to harden schools and a high-stakes special election. Republican lawmakers are openly discussing a bill to limit Mr. Trump’s trade powers, as some worry about economic repercussions or retaliation from trading partners.
